@wp.kernel
def expr_cbowox(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = float(0.0)
    v2 = float(1.0)
    tmp = float(0.0)
    v2 = (wp.cos(v2) / (wp.exp(v1 + 0.34) / (tmp + 0.71 / tmp + 0.92)))
    v2 = wp.cos((wp.exp(tmp + 0.87) / wp.cos(v1 + 0.09)))
    v0 = (tmp + ((v2 + 0.63 - tmp + 0.88) / tmp))
    v1 = wp.cos((wp.cos(tmp + 0.63) / (v2 + 0.94 - tmp + 0.62)))
    data[tid] = v0
